To make in Linux, make sure the development packages for SDL, SDL_image and SDL_gfx are installed, then type "make"

To make in Windows, try the above with mingw32

Running simulation: run the sim executable with the maze image as the first parameter:
    Linux:	./sim maze1.png
    Windows:	sim maze1.png


To program in avrdude: 'sudo avrdude -p m8 -c bsd -D -U flash:w:main.hex'

In windows use something else, programmer type is "BSD"